Package org.sd.text.radixtree

Interface Summary
RadixTree<T> Interface for a radix or Patricia trie.
ValueMerger<T> An interface for resolving conflicts while building a radix tree.
ValueReplicator<T> An interface for duplicating an instance of a value for placement into nodes inserted for splits.
Visitor<T> Visitor interface used by RadixTreeImpl for performing tasks on a searched node.
 

Class Summary
GeneralizedSuffixTree Implementation of a generalized suffix tree using a radix tree.
RadixData<T> Data to hold in a radix tree node.
RadixTreeImpl<T> Implementation ported to use the org.sd.util.tree.Tree datastructure.
SuffixTree Implementation of Ukkonen's Suffix Tree Algorithm for inserting into a suffix tree in time O(n), where n is the length of the string to insert.
